---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Commercial Door Installation | Pocket Door Services"
  description="Professional commercial door installation services in Orlando, Miami & Fort Myers, FL. Automatic sliding doors, fire-rated doors, rolling steel doors. Call (954) 727-5410."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-primary text-white py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-20" style="background-image: url('/images/services/installation.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Commercial door installation service"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/95 to-primary/70"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-wide mb-4">Commercial Door Installation</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4 text-gray-200">Serving Orlando, Miami & Fort Myers, FL</p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Professional commercial door installation services critical for businesses seeking to enhance security, improve functionality, and maintain a professional appearance.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="tel:9547275410" class="bg-white text-primary font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-center" aria-label="Call Pocket Door Services">
            (954) 727-5410
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors text-center">
            FREE ESTIMATE
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide text-primary mb-4">Expert Commercial Door Installation</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Commercial door installation is critical for businesses seeking to enhance security, improve functionality, and maintain a professional appearance. Our team specializes in the installation of automatic sliding doors, fire-rated doors, rolling steel doors, and a wide range of commercial door systems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Every installation begins with a thorough assessment of your space and requirements. We ensure precise frame alignment, accurate measurements, and the use of quality hardware to guarantee long-lasting performance. Our technicians work efficiently to minimize disruption to your business operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The benefits of professional commercial door installation include enhanced security, improved energy efficiency, and reduced operational expenses. Properly installed doors contribute to a safer, more efficient workplace while projecting a professional image to clients and visitors.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/services/installation.webp" alt="Commercial door installation service" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Why Choose Pocket Door Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Fast & Reliable", icon: "M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" },
          { name: "Transparent Pricing", icon: "M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Emergency 24/7", icon: "M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Expert Technicians", icon: "M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" },
        ].map((f) => (
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={f.icon} /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg tracking-wide text-primary">{f.name}</h3>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Services -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Our Other Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Roller Replacement & Frame Repair", href: "/service/roller-replacement-and-frame-repair", image: "/images/services/roller-replacement.webp" },
          { name: "Lock Repair", href: "/service/lock-repair", image: "/images/services/lock-repair.webp" },
          { name: "Hinge Repair/Replacement", href: "/service/hinge-repair-replacement", image: "/images/services/hinge-repair.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Repair", href: "/service/commercial-door-repair", image: "/images/services/repair.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Lock Services", href: "/service/commercial-door-lock-services", image: "/images/services/lock-services.webp" },
        ].map((s) => (
          <a href={s.href} class="group bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-border/30">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
              <img src={s.image} alt={`${s.name} service`} class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl tracking-wide text-primary">{s.name}</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide mb-4">Need Commercial Door Installation?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Contact our expert technicians today for professional commercial door installation services in Orlando, Miami, and Fort Myers. We install all types of commercial doors.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:9547275410" class="inline-flex bg-accent text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Call Now (954) 727-5410</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors">FREE ESTIMATE</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
